00:42:43,480 --> 00:42:49,010
never imagine themselves better or more accomplished than someone without these gifts. And those

688
00:42:49,010 --> 00:42:54,450
of us who marvel at these gifts shouldn't imagine that that person who God uses to bring healing

689
00:42:54,450 --> 00:43:01,660
and exorcism and deliverance and prophecy and speaking in other tongues is a super Christian

690
00:43:01,660 --> 00:43:12,940
that we need to worship. Always worship the giver, never the gifted. Always worship the giver,

691
00:43:13,060 --> 00:43:21,450
never the gift. In the end, for the body to work, it needs all its parts. In good health,

692
00:43:21,450 --> 00:43:23,470
working without jealousy or

693
00:43:23,470 --> 00:43:25,330
silly pride to that same

694
00:43:25,330 --> 00:43:27,740
final goal, which is carrying

695
00:43:27,740 --> 00:43:28,820
out the will of God on earth.

696
00:43:30,460 --> 00:43:32,660
Now let me read you this anecdote before we close

697
00:43:32,660 --> 00:43:34,380
because it describes somebody who's

698
00:43:34,380 --> 00:43:36,460
pretty heavily weighted

699
00:43:36,460 --> 00:43:38,480
in these so-called power

700
00:43:38,480 --> 00:43:40,880
gifts. And it describes

701
00:43:40,880 --> 00:43:44,290
her strengths and

702
00:43:44,290 --> 00:43:47,560
her weaknesses. Her name is

703
00:43:47,560 --> 00:43:49,620
Lucia from Argentina. I don't know if that's her

704
00:43:49,620 --> 00:43:51,970
real name. Christian Schwartz

705
00:43:51,970 --> 00:43:53,970
writes, I've met Lucia

706
00:43:53,970 --> 00:43:56,010
at two different conferences. Both

707
00:43:56,010 --> 00:44:00,310
time she was involved in a powerful ministry of intercession, and I suspect that most of

708
00:44:00,310 --> 00:44:05,230
the participants could sense the difference it made when a meeting was upheld by prayer

709
00:44:05,230 --> 00:44:12,320
warriors like her. At the same time, Lucia gave some of the other co-workers the impression

710
00:44:12,320 --> 00:44:18,710
that they were less spiritual than herself. Even if she never intended to communicate

711
00:44:18,710 --> 00:44:24,710
this, Christian, meaning the author, Christian Schwartz, the only thing that we can do for

712
00:44:24,710 --> 00:44:31,030
the church development is prayer. She told me time and again, and I always replied, Lucia,

713
00:44:31,650 --> 00:44:36,950
your prayer ministry is wonderful, but according to God's will, prayer is definitely not the only

714
00:44:36,950 --> 00:44:43,610
thing that we can and should do. Despite my words, I had the impression that while listening to me,

715
00:44:43,670 --> 00:44:47,770
she was really thinking, as convincing as it might sound, what Christian is teaching about

716
00:44:47,770 --> 00:44:55,690
church development is not what really matters. It's all prayer. To avoid misunderstanding, I must

717
00:44:55,690 --> 00:44:59,570
affirm that Lucia is a great woman and her ministry is powerfully used by God.

718
00:44:59,930 --> 00:45:03,150
I would not suggest that she withdraw one inch from her prayer ministry.

719
00:45:03,450 --> 00:45:07,590
Quite the contrary. However, instead of presenting prayer

720
00:45:07,590 --> 00:45:11,840
as an alternative to the gifts that we've heard about

721
00:45:11,840 --> 00:45:16,330
prior to this Sunday. The gifts of helps and administration

722
00:45:16,330 --> 00:45:20,270
and leadership and mercy and artistic creativity and on and on.

723
00:45:20,890 --> 00:45:23,230
The blue gifts. I mean the red gifts and the green gifts.

724
00:45:24,380 --> 00:45:27,380
I would suggest that it is important for her, Lucia,

725
00:45:27,500 --> 00:45:30,900
to appreciate the spiritual relevance

726
00:45:30,900 --> 00:45:33,480
and the spiritual power

727
00:45:33,480 --> 00:45:35,500
and the spiritual source

728
00:45:35,500 --> 00:45:38,280
of all dimensions of ministry.

729
00:45:40,500 --> 00:45:40,820
Let's pray.

730
00:45:45,470 --> 00:45:49,700
Father God, we want to serve you.

731
00:45:50,920 --> 00:45:53,780
And we want to do it in a way that pleases you.

732
00:45:53,840 --> 00:45:56,060
We want to do it according to the way that you've made us.

733
00:45:56,620 --> 00:45:58,160
We want to do it without jealousy,

734
00:45:58,780 --> 00:45:59,780
without second guessing.

735
00:46:00,580 --> 00:46:03,880
We want to do it relying on each other's strengths

736
00:46:03,880 --> 00:46:07,230
and forgiving each other's weaknesses.

737
00:46:09,010 --> 00:46:10,590
Father God, I ask that your Holy Spirit

738
00:46:10,590 --> 00:46:13,110
would move in this church in various ways.

739
00:46:14,030 --> 00:46:16,430
It would move in each person as they are gifted

740
00:46:16,430 --> 00:46:19,950
and that we would be one no matter what our gift.

741
00:46:21,080 --> 00:46:22,640
And I pray a blessing on these people

742
00:46:22,640 --> 00:46:26,240
as they chase hard after you and your will

743
00:46:26,240 --> 00:46:27,740
and your purpose for their life.

744
00:46:27,740 --> 00:46:31,900
I pray that they would find joy and peace and purpose

745
00:46:31,900 --> 00:46:34,360
in the life that you have for them.

746
00:46:35,640 --> 00:46:38,180
I pray all these things in the name of your Son, Jesus Christ.

747
00:46:38,900 --> 00:46:39,180
Amen.

748
00:46:40,480 --> 00:46:42,000
I want to make one more plug.

749
00:46:42,120 --> 00:46:42,960
October 6th.

